The paper discusses software architecture reconstruction and refactoring, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The framework described in the paper involves analyzing and migrating source code, which could also fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and software development (cs.SD) sub-categories. The use of automatic analysis and implementation suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
